All contributors implicitly agree to the [Contributor License Agreement](docs/CONTRIBUTING.md) by submitting pull requests.

## Privacy and Data Rights

While this software license covers the code, please note:
- User data rights are governed by our [Privacy Policy](docs/PRIVACY.md)
- BreathEasy collects no user data (privacy by design)
- All user data remains on the user's device
- No data rights conflicts exist with this open source license

